ccept bribes to turn a nelson's eye to crime. The City Police are assigned the task of apprehending a customed man called \"Shahenshah\", who operates at night and targets, tries and kills gangsters in a \"Judge and Executioner \"style. No one knows the real identity of Shahenshah, as he is feared by the police department, and respected by the poor and middle-class."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"国王","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"维贾的父亲因一桩银行抢劫案，被诬陷为索贿，含冤自杀而死。维贾长大后，当上了一名警长，表面上，他收受贿赂，徇私枉法，迷惑JK犯罪团伙；暗地里他化装为沙亨沙，为老百姓申张正义，为父亲洗刷冤屈，最终将恶人绳之以法，同时也赢得了沙露的爱情。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"義警神威","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"義警神威","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"維賈的父親因一樁銀行搶劫案，被誣陷為索賄，含冤自殺而死。維賈長大後，當上了一名警長，表面上，他收受賄賂，徇私枉法，迷惑 JK 犯罪團伙；暗地裏他化裝為沙亨沙，為老百姓申張正義，為父親洗刷冤屈，最終將惡人繩之以法，同時也贏得了沙露的愛情。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":1370,"adult":false,"title":"Rambo III","video":false,"overview":"Combat has taken its toll on Rambo, but he's finally begun to find inner peace in a monastery. When Rambo's friend and mentor Col. Trautman asks for his help on a top secret mission to Afghanistan, Rambo declines but must reconsider when Trautman is captured.","genre_ids":[28,12,53,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.1084,"vote_count":3405,"poster_path":"/uycbt9iVlAnKkQIisqUWuO8hVcm.jpg","release_date":"1988-05-24","vote_average":6.199,"backdrop_path":"/Afkcvov0y7osi6NwubwpPL6pfrA.jpg","original_title":"Rambo III","original_language":"en"},{"id":630004,"adult":false,"title":"The Vault","video":false,"overview":"Madrid, Spain, 2010. While the whole city follows the national team's successful participation in the World Cup, a group of daring thieves look for a way into one of the most secure and guarded places on the planet.","genre_ids":[18,28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.5894,"vote_count":1044,"poster_path":"/kWhXubAiIcHW0xn5GThflqaKZqh.jpg","release_date":"2021-03-04","vote_average":6.808,"backdrop_path":"/s1ohP4iE2Lg2TVBJILOkbTsGGgu.jpg","original_title":"Way Down","original_language":"en"},{"id":11854,"adult":false,"title":"Kuch Kuch Hota Hai","video":false,"overview":"Per her mother's last wish, an 8 year old girl sets out to reunite her father with his college best friend who was in love with him.","genre_ids":[10749,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.0931,"vote_count":421,"poster_path":"/5FmtHHDGPofW5Zjns1EM1D8503c.jpg","release_date":"1998-10-16","vote_average":7.5,"backdrop_path":"/iQJZMLr5cdn7Al2Av4V1VEzPDoQ.jpg","original_title":"कुछ कुछ होता है","original_language":"hi"},{"id":268,"adult":false,"title":"Batman","video":false,"overview":"Having witnessed his parents' brutal murder as a child, millionaire philanthropist Bruce Wayne fights crime in Gotham City disguised as Batman, a costumed hero who strikes fear into the hearts of villains. But when a deformed madman known as 'The Joker' seizes control of Gotham's criminal underworld, Batman must face his most ruthless nemesis ever while protecting both his identity and his love interest, reporter Vicki Vale.","genre_ids":[14,28,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.8387,"vote_count":8411,"poster_path":"/cij4dd21v2Rk2YtUQbV5kW69WB2.jpg","release_date":"1989-06-21","vote_average":7.232,"backdrop_path":"/zlsaQEE26TS34ziXAiNIAqa0MLX.jpg","original_title":"Batman","original_language":"en"},{"id":475557,"adult":false,"title":"Joker","video":false,"overview":"During the 1980s, a failed stand-up comedian is driven insane and turns to a life of crime and chaos in Gotham City 