":"Birds of Prey (and the Fantabulous Emancipation of One Harley Quinn)","original_language":"en"},{"id":65,"adult":false,"title":"8 Mile","video":false,"overview":"For Jimmy Smith, Jr., life is a daily fight just to keep hope alive. Feeding his dreams in Detroit's vibrant music scene, Jimmy wages an extraordinary personal struggle to find his own voice - and earn a place in a world where rhymes rule, legends are born and every moment… is another chance.","genre_ids":[18,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.338,"vote_count":7688,"poster_path":"/7BmQj8qE1FLuLTf7Xjf9sdIHzoa.jpg","release_date":"2002-11-08","vote_average":7.14,"backdrop_path":"/jNG7pl0DkN1nzxnbZj4MCGf2VEG.jpg","original_title":"8 Mile","original_language":"en"},{"id":490132,"adult":false,"title":"Green Book","video":false,"overview":"Tony Lip, a bouncer in 1962, is hired to drive pianist Don Shirley on a tour through the Deep South in the days when African Americans, forced to find alternate accommodations and services due to segregation laws below the Mason-Dixon Line, relied on a guide called The Negro Motorist Green Book.","genre_ids":[18,35,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.5064,"vote_count":12605,"poster_path":"/7BsvSuDQuoqhWmU2fL7W2GOcZHU.jpg","release_date":"2018-11-16","vote_average":8.222,"backdrop_path":"/5En0fmDagt3Pk8d7P3uTwfeQceg.jpg","original_title":"Green Book","original_language":"en"},{"id":359940,"adult":false,"title":"Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri","video":false,"overview":"After seven months have passed without a culprit in her daughter's murder case, Mildred Hayes makes a bold move, painting three signs leading into her town with a controversial message directed at Bill Willoughby, the town's revered chief of police. When his second-in-command Officer Jason Dixon, an immature mother's boy with a penchant for violence, gets involved, the battle between Mildred and Ebbing's law enforcement is only exacerbated.","genre_ids":[80,18],"media_type":"movie","popul