,"video":false,"overview":"Sandeep Malhotra comes to London to convince his girlfriend to give him another chance. Meanwhile, Siddharth, an undercover MI5 agent, receives a CD, which contains the recording of his kidnapped wife, Richa, and is asked to follow the instructions.","genre_ids":[53,28],"popularity":0.1876,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/r3n9To0WxMrLiiPLw5KEl4N7Qn0.jpg","release_date":"2007-10-19","vote_average":3.3,"backdrop_path":"/74YLebM0t59m1VHCvXb5eIxCdNO.jpg","original_title":"Speed","original_language":"hi"},{"id":1252470,"adult":false,"title":"Sikandar Ka Muqaddar","video":false,"overview":"After an unsolved diamond heist, a hard-nosed cop’s pursuit of his key suspect turns into obsession, until they finally face each other — and the truth.","genre_ids":[53,80,9648,28],"popularity":0.9917,"vote_count":54,"poster_path":"/eWUh4rgxtgypgnOa6uGMnUt01ux.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-29","vote_average":5.6,"backdrop_path":"/sv3clpwOSSZO1c8i9uX4zig6Lzz.jpg","original_title":"सिकंदर का मुकद्दर","original_language":"hi"},{"id":464018,"adult":false,"title":"Geetaa Mera Naam","video":false,"overview":"The film tells the story of four children who are separated at a fair and unknowingly reunite years later when Geeta (Sadhana) meets Nita (also Sadhana) in prison. Nita has been wrongly accused of murder. Geeta is then caught up in a scheme to find the true killer which leads her to her brother Johnny's (Sunil Dutt) gang.","genre_ids":[28,18,53],"popularity":0.1154,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/4IXbIjPQYNH4F7BVeMfr3mqWdts.jpg","release_date":"1974-03-24","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/yaXeAd9Gw2Fov6pcCL5HPPrNQtE.jpg","original_title":"Geetaa Mera Naam","original_language":"hi"},{"id":272565,"adult":false,"title":"Mrityudand","video":false,"overview":"Ketki marries Vinay, who is exploited by hard-nosed businessman Tirpat. Ketki then organizes local women against Tirpat & Co. Her group includes her sister-in-law, who had a run-in with a dangerous priest.","genre_ids":[28,18],"popularity":0.2133,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/jK9Mg1Of6fsJ6YPPWoEb0Ezj7HF.jpg","release_date":"1997-07-11","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Mrityudand : Death Sentence","original_language":"hi"},{"id":272662,"adult":false,"title":"Tirangaa","video":false,"overview":"After having witnessed the gruesome murder of his father, Harish's plans for revenge go for a toss when he is framed by the same mafia boss who killed his father.","genre_ids":[18,80,28,53],"popularity":0.3175,"vote_count":13,"poster_path":"/zA8lbSRKUpmCcHmD4WE8SUloTKa.jpg","release_date":"1993-01-29","vote_average":5.769,"backdrop_path":"/mQi6o11rJb3OZt3x14PzpIT8Ik2.jpg","original_title":"तिरंगा","original_language":"hi"},{"id":272668,"adult":false,"title":"Salaakhen","video":false,"overview":"Separated by tragedy, two virtually inseparable childhood friends meet again, only to fall in love this time.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":0.271,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/gIKtw9IBEupv4j95pF6BEvgco0L.jpg","release_date":"1975-12-26","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/rXT36L9MnyTJjwAohqcgqXjXIYM.jpg","original_title":"सलाखें","original_language":"hi"},{"id":274515,"adult":false,"title":"Muqabla","video":false,"overview":"Govinda and Aditya Pancholi star in this powerful tale about two brothers whose love for each is greater than any other bond. While manipulative orphan Karisma (Karisma Kapoor) falls for Suraj (Govinda) and tricks him into marrying her, his sibling, Deepak (Pancholi), is busy with a love of his own. In the meantime, scheming underworld kingpin Khanna (Shakti Kapoor) is doing his best to tear Suraj and Deepak apart.","genre_ids":[28,10749],"popularity":0.306,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1993-05-14","vote_average":3.5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Muqabla","original_language":"hi"},{"id":278557,"adult":false,"title":"Mawaali","video":false,"overview":"Nisha Verma's relatives wish that she would marry her cousin in order to keep the wealth in the family, but instead, she falls for an unapproved man named Ramesh, who is later accused of murdering her father. Having witnessed her lover at the scene of the crime, Nisha testifies against Ramesh, who's sentenced to death. But she's plagued by questions about why Ramesh was in her house and whether, in fact, he was responsible for her father's death.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":3.4553,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/3mwgs7UOcqSyt3pgHs05sXJxDSw.jpg","release_date":"1983-11-04","vote_average":2.5,"backdrop_path":"/jfL3x3ySXETDoaX2ySn3AYkbZ0k.jpg","original_title":"Mawaali","original_language":"hi"},{"id":472123,"adult":false,"title":"Golmaal Again","video":false,"overview":"Gopal and his best friends are back again, and this time they move back to their old neighborhood in a new palatial house where they learn that it is being haunted by a ghost.","genre_ids":[35,27,28,14],"popularity":0.5928,"vote_count":109,"poster_path":"/kGx26PL1v658T8XbOk5MfmNpHU3.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-20","vote_average":5.4,"backdrop_path":"/2JTqYozAkCUga9LSq64gI9CJ8Bm.jpg","original_title":"गोलमाल अगेन","original_language":"hi"},{"id":472138,"adult":false,"title":"Thugs of Hindostan","video":false,"overview":"After the British company’s officer Clive takes over the kingdom of Mirza, Princess Zafira and Khudabaksh aka Azaad form a band of rebel pirates who swear to defeat the English officer and win their freedom back. The British Company in return, hire the wily thug Firangi track Azaad’s gang and thwart his plans.","genre_ids":[12,28],"popularity":0.669,"vote_count":119,"poster_path":"/eonEvymAPpXvWvbBu21HYJx8VdS.jpg","release_date":"2018-11-07","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/qFfcH6T5QkBHKFJd3n3YrQA4ekS.jpg","original_title":"Thugs of Hindostan","original_language":"hi"},{"id":471919,"adult":false,"title":"Lucknow Central","video":false,"overview":"After being accused of murder and awaiting his death penalty, Kishen Mohan Girhotra is compelled by NGO worker Gayatri Kashyap to form a musical band of prisoners to compete at band competition held at the dreaded jail of ‘Lucknow Central’. Kishen befriends and convinces a talented bunch of criminals to form a band that provides them with a purpose and a new lease of life.","genre_ids":[18,28,53],"popularity":0.1621,"vote_count":30,"poster_path":"/gnGl9Djk4JCzJwFF5BhiL7nXL9Z.jpg","release_date":"2017-09-15","vote_average":6.383,"backdrop_path":"/oY6qI9ouISQZI6KOXQHxFfdiKyC.jpg","original_title":"Lucknow Central","original_language":"hi"},{"id":474084,"adult":false,"title":"Aakhri Adaalat","video":false,"overview":"Inspector Amar Kaushal attempts to incarcerate wrong-doers in his society only lead to frustration when they are let off by the incompetence of the law and his superiors and seniors. Eventually Amar stands accused of killing several criminals and innocents which prompts him to take law into his own hands.","genre_ids":[28,80],"popularity":0.4961,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/x7lC9TpyGFdnNQAq6N94yxkBE9m.jpg","release_date":"1988-06-10","vote_average":4.667,"backdrop_path":"/vA5rJhvF4lzqIdiu1SiOG93vS4g.jpg","original_title":"आखिरी अदालत","original_language":"hi"},{"id":867821,"adult":false,"title":"Krishna Balram: Kalvakra","video":false,"overview":"Kalvakra is a mighty asura and is regarded as a living devil. He has a powerful army of millions and is invincible in battle due to a boon he enjoys. When his Army carry away Udho, his friends Krishna and Balram, along with Radha, undertake the journey by sea to Kalvakra's island kingdom, upset Kalvakra's plans to capture them, mange to free Udho and get him safely back to Vrindavan.","genre_ids":[16,28,12],"popularity":0.1085,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/pnouMD9EqYsqC4eDSqPxrgQdBb4.jpg","release_date":"2010-04-17","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/mtn6BJrMxjiVRuK57n9nhxiiTYB.jpg","original_title":"Krishna Balram: Kalvakra","original_language":"hi"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt0093949","twitter_id":null